00:02:28.278 --> 00:02:35.018
On July 20th, 1969 , the United States of America became the first country to put

00:02:35.048 --> 00:02:40.448
a man on the moon, when Neil Armstrong stepped out of the Apollo Lunar Module and

00:02:40.518 --> 00:02:47.268
